                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for S Buisson &amp;lt;sbuisson@ddn.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/c5974c35-f25d-4466-986c-de5fc4647d6c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/c5974c35-f25d-4466-986c-de5fc4647d6c&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;test_79 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;test_79 failed with 2
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Whole test log is:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;== sanity-quota test 79: access to non-existed dt-pool/info doesn&apos;t cause a panic ========================================================== 22:36:58 (1642545418)
CMD: trevis-76vm4 touch /tmp/f79.sanity-quota
Creating new pool
CMD: trevis-76vm4 while [ -e /tmp/f79.sanity-quota ]; do /usr/sbin/lctl get_param -n qmt.lustre-QMT0000.dt-qpool1.info &amp;amp;&amp;gt;/dev/null; done
CMD: trevis-76vm4 lctl pool_new lustre.qpool1
trevis-76vm4: Pool lustre.qpool1 created
CMD: trevis-76vm4 lctl get_param -n lod.lustre-MDT0000-mdtlov.pools.qpool1 				2&amp;gt;/dev/null || echo foo
CMD: trevis-38vm2.trevis.whamcloud.com lctl get_param -n lov.lustre-*.pools.qpool1 		2&amp;gt;/dev/null || echo foo
CMD: trevis-76vm4 rm /tmp/f79.sanity-quota
pdsh@trevis-38vm2: trevis-76vm4: ssh exited with exit code 2
 sanity-quota test_79: @@@@@@ FAIL: test_79 failed with 2
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;





